            <div class="title">
                Pensions For Members Of The House Of Commons
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1939-02-02/debates/a02e3229-1f67-4ea4-a6c0-4ddea8b278fa/HighCourtOfJustice(KingSBenchDivision)" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
