            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-c94b0785-88d7-4027-8493-b68c8ff7b044">
                Mr. Buchanan
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
