    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">I did not say that the amount was due to Members not drawing salaries. It arises from lapses of time pending by-elections.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-32e6c2c6-20bd-4671-9d59-aba67b86c547" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
