        <div class="statement col-md-9  content-container " id='contribution-16c0e498-9223-4bbb-ab78-94f7c4921bc1'>
            
<p class="">Resolved,</p><p class=""> <blockquote><q>"That this House approves the recommendations of the Departmental Committee on Pensions for Members of the House of Commons and is in favour of the initiation of legislation to carry out its proposals which impose no charge upon the taxpayer."</q></blockquote></p>
